# Vue Dashboard Project

This project is a dashboard application built with Vue and Tailwind CSS.

## Goal
Create a clean, responsive, and reusable dashboard UI with modular Vue components.

## Tech Stack
- Vue 3
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Vue Router
- Pinia (for state management)

## Planned Dashboard Features
- App header and sidebar navigation
- Dashboard overview page
- Statistic cards and quick metrics
- User menu and profile section
- Reusable shared UI components

## Folder Focus
Main implementation will be inside:
- src/views/dashboard
- src/components/shared
- src/components/ui

## Next Step
Start by building the base dashboard layout (Header + Sidebar + Content area), then add widgets and reusable cards.
